quran[64]{c,v,t}:
  84,1,Jab asman phat jaey ga
  84,2,Aur apney rab kay hokum per kan lagaey ga aur issi kay laiq wo hay
  84,3,Aur jab zameen (khench ker)phela di jaey gi
  84,4,Aur iss mein jo hai ussay wo ugal degi aur khali hojaigi
  84,5,Aur apney rab ky hokoom per kaan lagaye gi aur isi kay laeeq wo hy
  84,6,Aey insaan! Tu apney rab say milney tak yeh koshish aur tamam kaam aur mehnatein kerky ussymulaqatkerney wala hy
  84,7,To(us waqt) jis shaks kydahaney hath mein aamaal naama diya jaiyga
  84,8,Us ka hisab to bari aasani say liya jaey ga
  84,9,Aur wo apney ehal ki taraf hansi khushi lot ayega
  84,10,Han jis shaks ka aamaal nama us ki peeth ky peechy say diya jaey ga
  84,11,To wo maut ko bulaney lagyga
  84,12,Aur bharakti hui jahanum meindakhil hoga
  84,13,Yeh sahks apnay mutalqeen mein(duniya mein)khush tah
  84,14,Isska khayal tah kay Allah ki taraf loot ker hi na jaey ga
  84,15,Que nahi hanlankay iska rab usy bakhobi dekh raha tha
  84,16,mujhy shafaq ki qasam!aur rat ki
  84,17,Aur iski jama kerda chezon ki qasam
  84,18,Aur chand ki jab kay wo kamil hojata hay
  84,19,Yaqenan tum ik halat say dosri halat per phuncho gay
  84,20,Inhein ki hogaya kay iman nahi laty
  84,21,Aur jab in kay pass quran parha jata hay to sajda nahi kerty
  84,22,balky jinhon nay kufur kiya wo jhotla rahy hein
  84,23,aur Allah khob janta hay jo kuch yah dilon mein rakhty hein
  84,24,Inhen alamnak azabon ki khush khabri suna do
  84,25,Han eman walon aur nek amal walon be shumar aur na khtam honey wala ajar hay
  85,1,Burjoon waly asman ki qasam
  85,2,Wada kiey hoy din ki qasam
  85,3,Hazir honey waly aur hazir kiey hoy ki qasam
  85,4,(kay) kahndaqon waly halak kiey gay
  85,5,Wo ik aag thi endhan wali
  85,6,jab kay wo log uskay ass pass bethy thy
  85,7,Aur musalmano kay sath jo ker rahy thy us ko apney samney dekh rahy thy
  85,8,Yeh log in musalmano(kay kisi aur gunha ka)badla nahi lay rahy thy siway iskay wo Allah galib laeeq e hamd ki zat per iman laey thy
  85,9,jis kay liey asman o zameen ka mulk hay aur Allah Taalaa kay samney hy her chez
  85,10,Be-shak jin logon na musalman mardon aur auraton ko sataya phir tooba (bhi)na ki to unkay liey jahanum ka azab hay aur jalney ka azab hay
  85,11,Be-shak iman qabool kerney walo aur nek kam kerney walon kay liey wo baghat hein jin kay nechay nehrein beh rahi hein yehi bari kamyabi hay
  85,12,Yaqennan tery rab ki pukar bari sakht hay
  85,13,Wohi phyli martaba paida kerta hay aur wohi dobara paida kery ga
  85,14,Wo bara bakhsish kerney wala aur bohat mohabat kernay wala hay
  85,15,Arsh ka malik azmat wala hay
  85,16,jo chahy usy ker guzarney wala hay
  85,17,Tujhy lashkaron ki khabar bhi mili hay
  85,18,(Yani)firon aur samood ki
  85,19,(kuch nahi)balky kafir to jhotlaney mein pary hoy hein
  85,20,Aur Allah bhi unhein her taraf say ghery hoy hy
  85,21,Balkay yeh quran hay bari shan wala
  85,22,loh e mahfooz mein (likha hua) hay
  86,1,Qasam hay asman ki aur andhery mein roshan honay waly ki
  86,2,Tujhy maloom bhi hay ky wo raat ko namodar honey wali chez kiya hay
  86,3,Wo roshan sitara hay
  86,4,Koi asa nahi jis per nigheban farishta na ho
  86,5,Insan ko dekhna chaeiy kay kis chez say paida kiya gaya hay
  86,6,Wo ik uchalty pani say paida kiya hay
  86,7,Jo pait aur seney kay dirmiyan say nikalta hay
  86,8,Be sahk wo usy pher lyney per yaqeenan qudrat rakhney wala hay
  86,9,Jis din poshida bhedon ki janch partal hogi
  86,10,To na hoga uskay pass kuch zor na madadgar
  86,11,Barish waly asman ki qasam
  86,12,Aur pahtney wali zameen ki qasam
  86,13,Be-shak yeh (quran)albatta do tok faisla kerney wala kalam hai
  86,14,Yeh hansi ki(aur be faeeda) baat nahi
  86,15,Albatta kafir dao ghaat main nahi
  86,16,Aur mein bhi aik chaal chalraha hun
  86,17,Tu kafiron ko mohlat dey unhen thory dino chor dy